YOU can now keep your beverage cool while getting on with your business, without worrying about it getting warm when your busy with other stuff if you’re far away from your home refrigerator. The convenient mini-USB portable refrigerator can be used at home, from your laptop/PC or in your car. Not only does this fridge cool beverages, it also doubles as a warmer for coffee or tea.  ALSO READ: MUM MAKES OVER R300K SELLING HER BREAST MILK It can cool two cans or a bottle of beer at an average temperature of 10ºC to 15ºC. The heating temperature can reach up to 55ºC. The description on the website states that access to a USB interface takes five minutes and drops the minimum operating temperature in about half-an-hour’s time. The refrigerator is suitable for all PC or other USB interfaces.